<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Profile Approved</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f7fa;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4caf50 0%, #2e7d32 100%);
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .header .icon {
      font-size: 64px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
      color: #333333;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .success-box {
      background-color: #e8f5e9;
      border-left: 4px solid #4caf50;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4caf50 0%, #2e7d32 100%);
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 15px 40px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 25px 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      transition: transform 0.2s;
    }

    .button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .next-steps {
      background-color: #f0f7ff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }

    .next-steps h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #1976d2;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .next-steps ul {
      margin: 15px 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .next-steps li {
      margin: 10px 0;
      color: #555;
    }

    .footer {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #666666;
      font-size: 13px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: #4caf50;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .highlight {
      color: #4caf50;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #4caf50;
      color: white;
      padding: 5px 15px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .info-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 12px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    }

    .info-label {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #666;
    }

    .info-value {
      color: #333;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="icon">‚úÖ</div>
      <h1>Profile Approved!</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <div class="success-box">
        <p style="margin:0; font-size: 16px;">
          <strong>Hi {{name}},</strong>
        </p>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0;">
          Great news! Your candidate profile has been approved and is now <span class="badge">LIVE</span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <p>
        Your profile for <strong class="highlight">{{eventName}}</strong> has been reviewed and approved by our
        administration team. Voters can now view your profile and cast their votes!
      </p>

      <div style="background-color: #f9f9f9; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 25px 0;">
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Event:</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{eventName}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Approval Date:</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{formatDate approvalDate}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row" style="border-bottom: none;">
          <span class="info-label">Status:</span>
          <span class="info-value"><span class="badge">Approved</span></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="next-steps">
        <h3>üéØ What's Next?</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Monitor your progress</strong> - Check your vote count and statistics in your portal</li>
          <li><strong>Update campaign materials</strong> - Keep your profile fresh and engaging</li>
          <li><strong>Engage with voters</strong> - Your profile is now visible to all voters</li>
          <li><strong>Stay informed</strong> - We'll notify you of any important updates</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{profileUrl}}" class="button">View Your Profile</a>
      </div>

      <div style="background-color: #fff3e0; border-left: 4px solid #ff9800; padding: 15px; margin: 25px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px;">
          <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Important:</strong> Any changes you make to your profile will require re-approval. Your profile
          will be temporarily unpublished during the review process.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
        Good luck with your campaign! We're here to support you every step of the way.
      </p>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px; color: #999; font-size: 13px;">
        Best regards,<br>
        <strong>The ITFY E-Voting Team</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated email from <strong>ITFY E-Voting Platform</strong></p>
      <p>
        <a href="{{profileUrl}}">Candidate Portal</a> |
        <a href="{{eventUrl}}">View Event</a>
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top: 15px; color: #999;">
        ¬© {{formatDate currentYear}} ITFY E-Voting. All rights reserved.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>
